               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols.
                     2ra-99rb)
 I-1a) Commemorative notice for the 12th of Ḫǝdār (fols.
                     2ra-3vb); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 3vb)
 I-2) Introduction (fol. 4ra-7va)
                     I-1b) Homily by Timothy (Dumatewos), Patriarch of Alexandria for the 12th of
                     Ḫǝdār (fols. 7va-15vb); miracle (fols. 16ra-17rb)
 I-3) Commemorative
                     notice (fols. 17va-18ra); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 18ra-rb); homily by Patriarch
                     [Metropolitan] Yoḥannǝs the Orthodox for the 12th of Tāḫśāś [Miyāzyā] (fols.
                     18rb-23rb); miracle (fols. 23va-24rb) 
 I-4) Commemorative notice (fol.
                     24va-vb); ʿarke-hymn (fols. 24vb-25ra); homily by an anonymous author for Ṭǝrr
                     [Tāḫśāś] (fols. 23vb-31ra); miracle (fol. 31ra-vb)
 I-5) Commemorative
                     notice (fols. 31vb-32rb); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 32rb); homily by an anonymous author
                     for Yakkātit (fols. 32rb-35vb); miracle (fols. 35vb-36vb)
 I-6)
                     Commemorative notice (fol. 37ra); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 37ra-rb); homily by
                     [Severus] Patriarch of Antiochia for the 12th of Maggābit (fols. 37rb-53rb);
                     miracle (fols. 53rb-54va)
 I-7) Commemorative notice (fols. 54va-55ra);
                     ʿarke-hymn (fol. 55ra); homily [by Epiphanius, Metropolitan of Cyprus] for the
                     12th of Miyāzyā [Ṭǝrr] (fols. 55rb-61va); miracle (fols. 61va-63va)
 I-8)
                     Commemorative notice (fols. 63vb-64rb); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 64rb); homily by
                     Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of Ethiopia for the 12th of Gǝnbot (fols. 64rb-66rb);
                     miracle (fols. 66rb-67vb)
 I-9) Commemorative notice (fols. 68ra-69va);
                     ʿarke-hymn (fol. 69va); homily by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of Aksum (ʾAkʷǝsǝm)
                     [for Sane] (fols. 69va-76va); miracle (fols. 76va-78rb)
 I-10)
                     Commemorative notice (fol. 78rb-vb); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 78vb); homily by
                     Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs for Ḥamle (fols. 78vb-83va); miracle (fols. 84va-84va)
                     
 I-11) Commemorative notice (fol. 84va-vb); ʿarke-hymn (fols. 84vb-85ra);
                     homily by an anonymous author [for Naḥāse] (fols. 85ra-88rb); miracle (fols.
                     88rb-89va); 
 I-12) Commemorative notice (fol. 89va-vb); ʿarke-hymn (fol.
                     89vb); homily by an anonymous author for Maskaram (fols. 90ra-93rb); miracle
                     (fol. 93rb-vb)
 I-13) Commemorative notice (fols. 93vb-94vb); ʿarke-hymn
                     (fol. 94vb); homily by an anonymous author for Ṭǝqǝmt (fol. 94vb-98va); miracle
                     (fols. 98vb-99rb)
 II) Malkǝʾa Mikāʾel "Image of Michael" (fols.
                     99va-104rb) (cp. ChRep no. 119)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
