               <provenance>According to Additio 1, the Ms. was donated
                     by blatta Walda Māryām (of) May ʾAbʾa. His name and the name of his wife
                     Walatta ʾAnanya are mentioned in supplication formulas throughout Text I. The
                     names of their children are written at the end of Text I.</provenance></history>
